summary:
Seasoned and versatile geologist with extensive international industry experience. 
Expert in hands-on prospect evaluation and risk analysis. 
Developed the first successful geothermal energy projects in the Netherlands.

Specialties: Play-based exploration and Geographic Information Systems. Trained in multi-cultural skills; speaks several foreign languages.
